%2Fyoutu.be%2FMYGhTl-uqaY&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=38e6cba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MYGhTl-uqaY</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇人係唔知《香港人權與民主法案》到底係咩嚟？<br />\n用三分鐘睇晒條片佢！<br />\n唔係美國幫到咁仲唔知條法案係講啲咩啊嘛？<br />\n一陣去到中環比外媒問到口啞啞就真係好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">推晒比所有人睇到底條法案係幫緊我地啲咩！<br />\n仲有！<br />\n13：30遮打花園提早／準時到！叫晒身邊所有人去！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三分鐘了解《香港人權與民主法案》</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/MYGhTl-uqaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMYGhTl-uqaY&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=38e6cba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MYGhTl-uqaY</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">仲有冇人係唔知《香港人權與民主法案》到底係咩嚟？<br />\n用三分鐘睇晒條片佢！<br />\n唔係美國幫到咁仲唔知條法案係講啲咩啊嘛？<br />\n一陣去到中環比外媒問到口啞啞就真係好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推晒比所有人睇到底條法案係幫緊我地啲咩！<br />\n<br />\n仲有！<br />\n<br />\n13：30遮打花園提早／準時到！<br />\n<br />\n叫晒身邊所有人去！</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【有片！】 到底《香港人權與民主法案》係咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1551225/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1551225/page/1</a></div>"},{"pid":"a8c941257af3a641195120e9ae8a1f82cea7f91f","tid":1551152,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57da27efe00a5ddd30742325ac3977a4ed87099a","tid":1551152,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"FYY呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"係我床邊訓緊"